I"d<p>Since AppStrap 2.4 drop down menus show on hover. 
When adding new drop down menus simply add <code>data-bs-toggle="dropdown" data-bs-hover="dropdown"</code> to the trigger link make them show on hover instead of click.
For submenus you should include <code>data-close-others="false"</code> so the parent menu is not closed when hovering a submenu.</p>
